Integrated Polytechnic Regional College Ngoma (IPRC Ngoma) ni ishuri rikuru  ry’imyuga n’ubumenyingiro mu [[Rwanda]] – Koleji ya Ngoma nimwe mumashuri makuru agize Rwanda Polytechnic. IPRC-NGOMA (yahoze yitwa ETO Kibungo) yashinzwe mu 1989 na guverinoma y'u Rwanda. Mu 1994 mugihe cya jenoside yakorewe abatutsi ishuri ryafunze imiryango. Mu Gushyingo 2012, nibwo ishuri ryisumbuye rya Tekinike rya Kibungo ryazamuwe mu kigo cya Integrated Polytechnic Regional Centre (IPRC) mu Ntara y'Iburasirazuba na guverinoma y'u Rwanda.<ref>https://www.iprcngoma.rp.ac.rw/</ref><ref>https://schoolsinrwanda.com/listing/integrated-polytechnic-regional-college-ngomaiprc-ngoma/</ref>
